room_title: Escape room "The Norwegian Job" by Escape Challenge in Rochester (MN)
room_description:
On your last job in Oslo, Norway, a team member turned the table and stole the loot for himself! He betrayed you and left you for dead, assuming you had no chance of survival. But he was wrong...
One year later, you've tracked Steve to his new home in Rochester, MN. You have secured a window of one hour to break into Steve's home office, but walked right into a trap! You must find the way to unlock the door from the inside before you are caught by Steve and his guards.
